metadata.name: The Ocean is the witness
metadata.description:
Have you ever thought of forgetting things that keep springing up in the mind ?
Have you ever thought of going to a place where no one knows your name ?
Have you ever thought of being on a shoreline, praying to the waves to set you free ?
Have you ever thought of being still in a rushing world, to dream of things to be ?

I have.

And sometimes it's in the lashing waves of colorful memories and colorless hopes that we find ourselves.
Alone in a colorful world, with nothing but the ocean as a witness for all my thoughts today..
